      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verified against published analytical solutions for beam bending and contact mechanics.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical verified against Timoshenko beam bending and Hertzian contact analytical solutions. Maximum deviation 0.3% for beam case, 1.1% for contact case. Both within acceptable tolerance."
