      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed under conditions representative of COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on same screw design and rod configuration as COU. ASTM F1717 protocol directly represents the regulatory submission test. Two-laboratory validation increases confidence in result reproducibility. Validation activities judged highly relevant to COU."
